library(nycflights13)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(tidyr)
df_merged <- merge(flights, weather, by = c("origin", "year", "month", "day", "hour"))
df_plot <- df_merged %>% 
  select(temp, dep_delay, origin)

ggplot(df_plot, aes(x = temp, y = dep_delay, color = origin)) +
  geom_point() +
  labs(title = "Scatter Plot of temp vs. dep_delay Colored by origin", x = "Temperature", y = "Departure Delay")
## Warning: Removed 8244 rows containing missing values (`geom_point()`).

df_plot <- df_plot %>%
  na.omit(temp) %>% 
  mutate(
    warm_cold = case_when(
      temp > 55 ~ "warm",
      TRUE ~ "cold"
    )
  )
ggplot(df_plot, aes(df_plot$warm_cold, df_plot$dep_delay, color = df_plot$warm_cold)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(title = "warm_cold vs departure delay", x = "warm_cold", y = "dep_delay")

df_merged2 <- left_join(flights, planes, by = "tailnum")
df_merged2 %>%
  group_by(manufacturer) %>% 
  summarise(av_dep_delay = mean(dep_delay, na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
  arrange(desc(av_dep_delay))

long_iris <- iris %>%
  pivot_longer(cols = -Species, names_to = "leaf_dimension", values_to = "measurement")
long_iris %>%
  group_by(Species, leaf_dimension) %>% 
  summarise(
    mean_measurement = mean(measurement),
    median_measurement = median(measurement),
    min_measurement = min(measurement),
    max_measurement = max(measurement),
    sd_measurement = sd(measurement)
  )

ggplot(long_iris, aes(x = long_iris$Species, y = long_iris$ measurement)) + 
  geom_boxplot()+
  geom_point(position = position_jitter(width = 0.2), color = "blue") +
  facet_wrap(~leaf_dimension, scales = "free_y")
